## 6. Sample Prompts Library

### 6.1 Session Opener

```
## Session Context
Project: RISKMIND_Underwriting_DEV
Date: 2026-06-01 | Session: Day 12
Focus: Add guardrails to Agent 5 (Compliance Checker)
Ref: See 03_SESSION_LOG.md for prior context
Last done: Completed Agent 4 output schema
Today goal: Build input validation layer for Agent 5
Output: Code only
```

### 6.2 End-of-Session Summary Request

```
End of session. Summarize in the standard format:
Decisions made, code produced, open questions, next start point.
Max 25 lines. I will append this to my 03_SESSION_LOG.md.
```

### 6.3 Resuming After a Gap (Multiple Days Away)

```
I'm resuming work on [Project Name] after [N] days.
I've re-read 03_SESSION_LOG.md. The last session ended at:
[paste NEXT line from last session entry]
Today I want to: [goal]
Output: Code only unless I ask otherwise.
```

### 6.4 Mid-Session Context Reset (When Chat Gets Long)

```
This conversation is getting long. Before we continue:
1. Summarize what we have built/decided so far in 10 lines
2. List the one thing we are currently solving
I will start a fresh chat with that summary.
```

### 6.5 Surgical Code Fix (Minimal Token Spend)

```
Fix only this function. No explanation. No refactoring of surrounding code.
Problem: [one sentence]

[paste the single function here]
```

### 6.6 Team Member Onboarding to a Project

```
You are joining project [Name] mid-stream.
Read 00_PROJECT_CONTEXT.md and 03_SESSION_LOG.md (already in this Project).
Your task today: [task]
Ask me only if something is missing from those files.
```

