## 9. Checklist — Every Session

- [ ] Open a **NEW chat** (do not reopen old threads)
- [ ] Paste your Context Card at the top
- [ ] Work — paste only what is relevant to the current task
- [ ] At end: run End-of-Session Summary Prompt
- [ ] Append summary to `03_SESSION_LOG.md`
- [ ] Update `04_OPEN_ITEMS.md` with any new open questions or resolved items
- [ ] Re-upload both files to Project knowledge base (replace old versions)

