## How Claude Reads Your Project Files

When you chat inside a Project, Claude automatically reads all uploaded knowledge base files at the start of every conversation. This means:

- You never need to paste `00_PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` — Claude already has it
- You never need to re-explain your stack, conventions, or domain
- The only thing you paste is your **Context Card** (the dynamic, session-specific part)
- The `03_SESSION_LOG.md` gives Claude memory of what happened in past sessions without you re-reading old chats

This is the entire point of the Project knowledge base — **stable context lives in files, dynamic context lives in the Context Card.**

